@startuml
title Sequence Diagram (Settings: Modifica Profilo e Cambio Password) - Iterazione 5

actor Utente                          as U
participant "Browser\n(React App)"    as FE
participant "SettingsPage"            as SP
participant "API Gateway\n(FastAPI)"   as GW
participant "Auth Controller"          as Ctrl
participant "Auth Service"             as Svc
participant "Profile Repository"       as Repo
participant "MongoDB Atlas"            as DB

' ─── 1. Apertura impostazioni ─────────────────────────────────
U   -> FE   : Clicca pulsante ⚙
FE  -> FE   : showSettings = true
FE  -> SP   : Render SettingsPage\n(userInfo, connectionStatus)
SP  -> SP   : Precompila form\ncon dati userInfo correnti

' ─── 2. Modifica Profilo ─────────────────────────────────────
U   -> SP   : Modifica campi\n(nome, cognome, dipartimento, corso, anno)
SP  -> SP   : Selezione dipartimento →\nfiltra corsi da DIPARTIMENTI_CORSI
SP  -> SP   : Selezione corso →\nauto-imposta tipologia

U   -> SP   : Clicca "Salva Modifiche"

SP  -> GW   : PUT /api/auth/profile\n[Cookie: access_token=<JWT>]\n{ name, surname, department,\ncourse, tipology, year }

GW  -> GW   : verify_token(cookie)\n→ estrae matricola
GW  -> Ctrl : update_profile(matricola, update_fields)
Ctrl -> Svc : updateProfile(matricola, update_fields)
Svc  -> Repo : findById(matricola)
Repo -> DB   : findOne({ matricola })
DB   --> Repo : user_doc
Repo --> Svc : user_doc

alt Utente trovato
  Svc  -> Repo : updateProfile(matricola, fields)
  Repo -> DB   : updateOne({ matricola },\n{ $set: fields })
  DB   --> Repo : result
  Repo -> DB   : findOne({ matricola })
  DB   --> Repo : updated_user
  Repo --> Svc : updated_user
  Svc  --> Ctrl : updated_user
  Ctrl -> Ctrl : _public_profile()\n(rimuove passwordHash)
  Ctrl --> GW  : { user (senza passwordHash) }
  GW   --> SP  : 200 OK + profilo aggiornato

  SP   -> FE   : onProfileUpdate(updatedData)
  FE   -> FE   : Aggiorna userInfo nello stato React
  SP   -> SP   : Mostra "Profilo aggiornato con successo!"

else Utente non trovato
  Svc  --> Ctrl : raise HTTPException(404)
  Ctrl --> GW  : 404 Not Found
  GW   --> SP  : errore
  SP   -> SP   : Mostra messaggio errore
end

' ─── 3. Cambio Password ──────────────────────────────────────
U   -> SP   : Compila form password\n(corrente, nuova, conferma)
SP  -> SP   : Validazione locale:\n- tutti i campi compilati\n- nuova password >= 6 char\n- nuova == conferma

U   -> SP   : Clicca "Cambia Password"

SP  -> GW   : PUT /api/auth/password\n[Cookie: access_token=<JWT>]\n{ current_password, new_password }

GW  -> GW   : verify_token(cookie)\n→ estrae matricola
GW  -> Ctrl : change_password(matricola, current, new)
Ctrl -> Svc : changePassword(matricola, current, new)
Svc  -> Repo : findById(matricola)
Repo -> DB   : findOne({ matricola })
DB   --> Repo : user_doc
Repo --> Svc : user_doc

alt Password corrente valida
  Svc  -> Svc  : bcrypt.checkpw(current, hash) → True
  Svc  -> Svc  : new_hash = bcrypt.hashpw(new, gensalt())
  Svc  -> Repo : updateProfile(matricola,\n{ passwordHash: new_hash })
  Repo -> DB   : updateOne({ matricola },\n{ $set: { passwordHash } })
  DB   --> Repo : result
  Repo --> Svc : result
  Svc  --> Ctrl : success
  Ctrl --> GW  : { status: "success",\nmessage: "Password aggiornata" }
  GW   --> SP  : 200 OK

  SP   -> SP   : Mostra "Password aggiornata con successo!"
  SP   -> SP   : Reset campi password

else Password corrente errata
  Svc  -> Svc  : bcrypt.checkpw(current, hash) → False
  Svc  --> Ctrl : raise HTTPException(401)
  Ctrl --> GW  : 401 Unauthorized
  GW   --> SP  : errore
  SP   -> SP   : Mostra "Password corrente non corretta"
end

@enduml
